# Group Recipient Validation

Recipient Validation is a tool for validating recipient email addresses. 
An address will either be returned as valid or invalid. 
Any invalid email address responses will also provide a reason why it is invalid.

### Single Address Validation [/recipient-validation/single/{address}]

+ Parameters
    + address (required, string, `valid@ddress.com`)

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: 14ac5499cfdd2bb2859e4476d2e5b1d2bad079bf

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "results": {
                "valid": true
            }
        }
